The paper deals with image generation using deep learning techniques, specifically Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves generating images that go beyond the boundaries of the original image, which could fall under the category of computer graphics (cs.GR). Additionally, the paper involves training a neural network, which could fall under the categories of multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
